high_descs: Exit this room through the path on the left, then turn right into the hall and take the last door on the left, approaching the dresser in the corner ahead.
Pick up the pencil from atop the dresser.
Exit this room the way you came in, turn right to go down the hall, then turn left where the hall stops into the kitchen area, stopping at the table with the cardboard box on it.
Put the pencil into the box.
Pick up the box with the pencil.
Turn around and look towards the counter with the plate and knife on it.
Place the box down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a pencil in it on a kitchen countertop.

Pick up the box with the pencil on it.

Keep the box on the top of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the pencil inside the box and keep it on the top of the countertop.
